'Lakshmi telah tiba.'

00:19:39.880 --> 00:19:40.920
'Ini gratis.'

00:19:41.000 --> 00:19:42.440
'Oh, cantik!'

00:19:42.760 --> 00:19:44.200
'Resi!  - Malishka!'

00:19:44.560 --> 00:19:45.720
'Aku sangat menyesal!'

00:19:46.120 --> 00:19:48.120
'Resi, ambil ini.
